Constructor Detail

LackeySVGraph

LackeySVGraph(java.lang.Object width, java.lang.Object height, java.lang.Object inst, java.lang.Object fPath, java.lang.Object verb, java.lang.Object oF, java.lang.Object percentile, java.lang.Object range, java.lang.Object pageSize, java.lang.Object gridMarks, java.lang.Object workingSetInst, java.lang.Object threads, java.lang.Object boost, java.lang.Object PLOTS)
Build various graphs from a lackeyml file
Parameters:
width - width of the graph in pixels
height - height of the graph in pixels
inst - graph instructions
fPath - path to the lackeyml file being processed
verb - verbose output
oF - name of reference map output file
percentile - percentile of memory to form base of reference map
range - range of memory to be examined in reference map
pageSize - bit shift used for pages (eg 12 for 4096KB pages)
gridMarks - number of grid marks to be used on graphs
workingSetInst - number of instructions against which to plot working set
threads - size of thread pool
boost - size of margin on graphs
PLOTS - bitmask for graphs to be drawn
